\f1\i\b We know that. Stop badgering us about that. The reason why the pastaOS logo is a ramen bowl is because both ramen and pasta are types of noodle dishes, hence the ramen bowl logo.\

\f0\i0\b0 "But Pear bankrupted themselves to make pastaOS!"\

